title: Is the the hardest crying alone?
pid: 3cff3b58-d7ca-4ae4-aaea-7e92d7e0dc59
body: |2-
  When I had to leave Colombia, Lorena and I cried together about it,
  together there and then over the phone. I also cried at least once
  alone as a result of thinking about the two of us.
  That crying alone was much more difficult.
